snippet.title: The Complete FALLOUT Timeline Explained!
snippet.description:
The Fallout franchise has a long and complex history and timeline that has been expanding its post-apocalyptic future ever since the original game’s release back in 1997. With 4 mainline games, a handful of spin-offs, and now a TV show that’s set within the same universe, the series has a big, meaty timeline to wrap your head around. And with the Amazon Prime TV show expanding on the franchise’s lore, and extending the timeline further into the future, there is no better time to dive back into the lore of Fallout than now.

This is the Fallout timeline fully explained.

From the Pre-War origins of RobCo. and Vault-Tec all the way through to Lucy MacLean’s journey to find her father via the stories set in the Capital Wasteland and the Commonwealth, this video breaks down the long and complex timeline of the Fallout franchise.

#TimelineExplained #Fallout #GameSpot

00:00 - INTRO
06:58 - FALLOUT 4 PROLOGUE - 2077
07:51 - FALLOUT (TV) - 2077
08:48 - FALLOUT 76 - 2102
12:09 - FALLOUT - 2161
14:38 - FALLOUT TACTICS - 2197
15:44 - FALLOUT 2 - 2241
18:20 - FALLOUT 3 PROLOGUE - 2258-2274
19:11 - FALLOUT 3 - 2277
25:01 - FALLOUT: NEW VEGAS - 2281
30:27 - FALLOUT 4 - 2287
35:37 - FALLOUT (TV SHOW) - 2296

snippet.title: Iran's attack on Israel 'will be met with a response', military chief confirms| ITV News
snippet.description:
Israel’s military chief said it will respond after Iran launched an extensive drone and missile attack on Saturday despite world leaders urging them not to retaliate.

Lt. Gen. Herzi Halevi said that Israel is still considering its steps, but confirmed the Iranian strike “will be met with a response.”

He did not mention when this response could happen.

snippet.title: Devin Haney & Ryan Garcia Have an Epic Conversation | One on One | GQ Sports
snippet.description:
Devin Haney and Ryan Garcia face-off Saturday, April 20 in Brooklyn, New York. Originally, we planned an epic face-to-face conversation with the fighters pre-match, but tensions are so high they wouldn't sit together. Instead, we've got exclusive separate interviews with both. Who has more drip? How long have they been rivals? Why did they agree to this fight? The title-defending lightweight champion Haney and the formidable Garcia offer their predictions for this fight and share some subtle digs about their readiness and strategies.

Director of Photography: AJ Young

Talent: Devin Haney; Ryan Garcia
Producer: Kristen DeVore
Senior Producer: Lizzy Halberstadt

snippet.title: DEVIN HANEY: MILLION DOLLAZ WORTH OF GAME EPISODE 269
snippet.description:
Devin Haney, a rising star in the world of boxing, returns to the Million Dollaz Worth Of Game podcast with a wealth of experiences to share. Haney’s career has been marked by determination, skill, and a relentless pursuit of excellence. His upcoming bout with Ryan Garcia on April 20, 2024, promises to be a clash of titans, and fans are eagerly awaiting this showdown.

In a recent episode, Haney took listeners on a tour of his opulent Las Vegas property, where he houses an impressive collection of cars valued at over 3 million dollars. Beyond the glitz and glamour, Haney delved into the heart of boxing. He candidly discussed how popularity, rather than pure skill, often dictates who earns the big paychecks in the sport.

But it’s Haney’s unique bond with his father that truly sets him apart. Unlike other father-son duos in boxing, their success hasn’t driven them apart; instead, it has brought them closer. Haney’s admiration for his father’s guidance and unwavering support shines through in every conversation.

Lastly, Haney shared his list of the top 5 boxers in the game today, along with his thoughts on who truly deserves a spot in the boxing Hall of Fame. His insights are a testament to his passion for the sport and his commitment to leaving a lasting legacy.

ABOUT CHELSEA FOOTBALL CLUB 

Founded in 1905, Chelsea Football Club is an English professional football club based in Fulham, West London with Stamford Bridge as the home of the club. Competing in the Premier League - the top division of English football, the club has had many successes, winning five Premier League titles. The club won their first major honour, the League championship in 1955, followed by the FA Cup in 1970, their first European honour, the Cup Winners' Cup in 1971, and became the third English club to win the Club World Cup in 2022. 

As the Pride of London, Chelsea FC is one of the most success clubs in terms of overall trophies won. They are the only club to have won all three major European competitions twice and have taken the crown domestically, winning six league titles, eight FA Cups, five League Cups, and four FA Community Shields. Internationally, Chelsea have won the UEFA Champions League, the UEFA Europa League, the UEFA Cup Winners' Cup and the UEFA Super Cup twice each, and the FIFA Club World Cup once since their inception.

The Chelsea YouTube channel provides access to all the build-up, training and behind-the-scenes moments and matchday action along with all the unseen edits and player focus from Reece James, Thiago Silva and Enzo Fernandez to Sam Kerr, Fran Kirby and many more. It’s the only channel where you’ll get an authentic look at this great club including memorable nights with world-class heroes such as Peter Osgood, Gianfranco Zola, Frank Lampard, John Terry, Didier Drogba & Eden Hazard.

snippet.description:
SALINA, N.Y. — It is now confirmed that a Syracuse police officer and an Onondaga County Sheriff's Office deputy were shot and killed in Salina Sunday night.

According to Syracuse Police Chief Joseph Cecile, the officer killed was on the job for about three years. Sheriff Toby Shelley described the deputy killed as a seasoned deputy.

Kellogg’s is teaming up with Minecraft ​⁠(@minecraft) to give you FREE Exclusive Character Creator Items to use in game when you buy any participating Kellogg’s cereals like Frosted Flakes, Froot Loops, Apple Jacks and Corn Pops.

Minecraft and Kellogg’s have partnered with the Arbor Day Foundation to build a better and greener world by planting 250,000 trees in forests of great need in the U.S. 
 
Visit https://arborday.org to learn more about the Arbor Day Foundation's tree planting mission.

• Select Kellogg cereals will include a FREE EXCLUSIVE DCL Minecraft Creator item, on specially-marked promotional cereal boxes.
• Get one FREE EXCLUSIVE Minecraft Character Creator item when you purchase any participating Kellogg’s cereal between now and 7/31/2024. Collect all 3 Character Creator items!
• Take a picture of your receipt and upload to https://www.wkkelloggpromotions.com/  (must be 16yrs+ to participate.)
• You can only select the character creator item once (cannot collect the same item more than once, no trading)
• Character Creator Items are exclusive to the U.S. to use in Minecraft game.
• Offer good through Kellogg’s redemption website: https://www.wkkelloggpromotions.com

snippet.title: Can You Beat DARK SOULS 2 With Only Scythes?
snippet.description:
I mean, they were overpowered in Dark Souls 1, surely that trend continued, right?
...guys?

The reaper run continues into Dark Souls 2 as we try to beat all the games bosses, while simultaneously eradicating the world of all NPC life. Place your bets now on whether the bosses or the NPCs were harder.

Can you beat Dark Souls 2 with only Scythes? Time to find out.

Hyrule Castle Courtyard - Zelda Ocarina of Time
Ruined Paths - Gravity Rush
Town 1 - Eiyuden Chronicle Rising
Goron City - Zelda Ocarina of Time
Praise the Lamb - Cult of the Lamb
Outset Island - Zelda Windwaker
Pond - Bugdom
Rainbow Road - Super Mario Kart

Katana Zero - Katana Zero

snippet.title: Chicago mass shooting: New details released
snippet.description:
Chicago police released new details after a child was killed and 10 other people were wounded at a family gathering on the South Side Saturday night. 

Officers responded to a Shotspotter alert in the 2000 block of West 52nd Street in the Back of the Yards neighborhood at 9:18 p.m. and found several victims with gunshot wounds. 

A witness told police that they saw a black sedan pull up and someone inside fired multiple shots into the crowd before fleeing southbound on Damen Avenue. 

A family was gathered for a birthday party outside when gunmen opened fire with assault rifles and handguns, according to a police report. There were 75 shell casings recovered from the scene, according to the report. The first officers at the scene began lifesaving measures, including applying tourniquets and chest seal bandages.

snippet.title: I Ran A Custom Croissant Bakery For A Day
snippet.description:
Try Headspace today for free: https://headspace-web.app.link/e/SF Use my code: SAFIYA60 - for a 60-day free trial of the app! Crunchy Quaso sleepcast when??

HELLO FRIENDS!! So, the internet loves croissants. And, coincidentally, so do I. So after falling down a cronut hole of croissant content - I decided, I needed to make some frickin croissants. And surprisingly, Black Box Bakery in Denver agreed to take me on as a pastry apprentice! Not only did I get a high-altitude pastry bootcamp - learning how to laminate my own dough, and roll my own classic croissants - but I also got to create my own custom, semi-goth, cream-filled croissant CUBE - that you can actually try at Black Box Bakery if you go there in person!! What do you think? Beetlejuice or beetleJUICY?

A big thank you to everyone at Black Box Bakery for helping us out with this video; make sure to check them out here! ​​https://www.blackboxbakery.com/
and https://www.instagram.com/blackbox_bakery/

If you’re interested in trying our custom croissant cube for yourself, they will be available Friday, Saturday, & Sunday for the next month! You can either pre-order the Safiya x Black Box Croissant online for pickup here https://order.toasttab.com/online/black-box-bakery-5505-w-20th-ave-unit-182 or visit Black Box Bakery in person while supplies last!

(this video is NOT sponsored by Black Box Bakery and we are not receiving any portion of their sales - they are just a cool small business we love!)

Check out our merch shop here!! https://fiendishbehavior.com 

My Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/safiyany/​
My TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@safiyany
My Snapchat: https://t.snapchat.com/3JJgsbuN
Tyler's channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCc6BTuuTzfMLKj_RgwuDnQw 
Our YouTube Shorts channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCLKQoTgt5BwFJJKWyeXHbig 

MUSIC

snippet.title: BREAKING: Iran launches “mass drone and missile attack” on Israel | BBC News
snippet.description:
In a dramatic escalation of the crisis in the middle east, Iran has launched a mass drone and missile attack on Israel..

Retaliation by Iran has been widely predicted, following an Israeli attack on the Iranian consulate in the Syrian capital Damascus.

Israel says its armed forces are on full alert with air defences prepared and combat planes in the air.

Jordan has declared a state of emergency.   President Biden has returned to the White House for crisis talks with national security advisers.

snippet.title: PESO COMPLETO (Video Oficial) - Peso Pluma, Arcángel
snippet.description:
PESO COMPLETO (Video Oficial) - Peso Pluma, Arcángel
Double P Records©

➸ ESCUCHA / LISTEN: https://orcd.co/n9jvvpq


➸Música 

Interpretación - Peso Pluma, Arcángel
Composición  - Hassan Emilio Kabande Laija,  Austin Santos, Carlos Dominguez Kenzo, Robert Rodriguez DM, Jorge Valdez, Dimelo Flow, Marvin Hawkins, Maff
Producción - Dimelo Flow, Maff


➸Video
Director @fernandolugo @pesopluma 
Creative @johndelacasa @pesopluma 
EP @buenavibra 
Producer @fabi.olive 
Local producer @meganshorttt 
Dop @sidsingh.dp 
PD @kaylinnduffy 
Edit @joanpabon_ 
Color @sidsingh.dp


➸Letra
Papi, oye lo que te voy a decir
Tu dices que tumbo
Si tu dices que el dinero no cambia a las personas
Simplemente no están haciendo dinero

Andamo’ en alta
El Peso con Arca
Vuela dinero
Estos cabrones los tengo chupando
Parecen hookeros
Voy pa’ veinte años dándoles palo
Como un pelotero
Y si me retiro les dejo Austincito 
Y también se jodieron

Andamo’ en alta
El Peso con Arca
Vuela dinero
Estos cabrones los tengo mamando
Parecen hookeros
Desde Jalisco me estoy quedando con el mundo entero
Yo soy artista pero vivo como un capo ranchero

Se juntó Pablo y Gustavo
En una finca contando los chavos
El primo de Peso Pluma
Cabrón yo soy peso pesado
Pa’ lo que roncan de Bravo
Yo me los como y los cago
Tengo una suite en Condado
Cuatro putas que me clavo
En Santurce soy Jordan en Chicago

Pa’ mis hijos las combis son Kith
Ronca y te dejamo’ sin front teeth
A mi siempre se me va la mano
Voy a cambiar mi apellido a Austin Smith

Tengo llena como tres caleta
El dinero se guarda en maletas
Tu me odias a mis tres puñetas
A quién tú se lo mamas a mi me respetas

Andamo’ en alta
El Peso con Arca
Vuela dinero
Estos cabrones los tengo chupando
Parecen hookeros
Voy pa’ 20 años dándole palo
Como pelotero
Y si me retiro les dejo Austincito 
Y también se jodieron

Ando en alta
El Peso con Arca
Vuela dinero
Estos cabrones los tengo mamando
Parecen hookeros
Desde Jalisco me estoy quedando con el mundo entero
Yo soy artista pero vivo como un capo ranchero

El primero fue Daytona
Nunca tuve fecas
Trabajé mil horas
Que sigan buscando
Pero no tuvieron la escuela de grandes personas
La que se navega, 4.5 llora
El que pegó su propia banda sonora
Ahora varios ya me prenden veladoras
La cuenta la mandan a la contadora
La cadena de infinito nunca se me traba la que traigo al cinto
Superona y 4.5 de Houston hasta Puerto Rico
De México es el chamaquito
Y aquí sigo firme cuento billetitos
Por eso yo nunca me agüito
Ni sufro por ningún culito

Quiero saber si a ustedes
Les gusta la música del señor Santos
El que empezó a hacer trap primero que todos
Este cabrón es un ídolo para mí
Que se escuche fuerte el grito para Arcángel

Andamo’ en alta
El Peso con Arca
Vuela dinero
Estos cabrones los tengo chupando
Parecen hookeros
Voy pa’ 20 años dándole palo
Como pelotero
Y si me retiro les dejo Austincito 
Y también se jodieron

Andamo’ en alta
El Peso con Arca
Vuela dinero
Estos cabrones los tengo mamando
Parecen hookeros
Desde Jalisco me estoy quedando con el mundo entero
Yo soy artista pero vivo como un capo ranchero






Peso Pluma

snippet.title: What Happened To The Nautilus?
snippet.description:
Get Nebula for just $2.50 a month here: https://go.nebula.tv/mustard

Watch More Mustard Videos & Support The Channel: https://nebula.tv/mustard

Thanks to Wesley Dobbs for providing logos on the Russian space mirror!  https://www.artstation.com/kingvangarh

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/MustardChannel
Mustard Merchandise: https://mustardchannel.com/
Twitter:  https://twitter.com/MustardVideos
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Mustard-109952378202335

For centuries, the North Pole remained elusive. Early attempts to reach it were primarily motivated by the search for a navigable route through the Arctic to Asia, known as the Northwest Passage. Later, explorers focused specifically on reaching the Pole itself. But for centuries, reaching it seemed impossible. The polar environment was extremely unforgiving. Located in the middle of the Arctic Ocean, the North Pole is covered by a vast expanse of sea ice which constantly changes due to wind, ocean currents and seasonal melts. Explorers tried to reach the pole using ships, dogsleds, and even traveling by foot. The first verified, and officially recognized expedition to reach the North Pole didn’t occur until 1926 (although several explorers claimed to have reached it earlier). It was first reached using the airship Norge, which flew overhead, but did not land on the surface.  

In the late 1920’s, accomplished explorer Sir Hubert Wilkins became convinced that a submarine would provide the ultimate means of reaching the North Pole. A submarine could travel for extended periods beneath the ice, avoiding the extreme hazards above which had caused earlier expeditions to fail. Carrying the latest scientific equipment, the submarine’s crew could conduct valuable meteorological, oceanographic, biological, magnetic, and spectrographic experiments.

Wilkin’s submarine would be called the Nautilus. It was a retired WW1-era submarine that had been extensively modified by renowned Naval Architect Simon Lake. The Nautilus featured a heavily reinforced bow, a shock absorber and sledge runners to protect it from collision with sea ice. A diving compartment and airlock was also added to allow divers to explore the depths while the submarine remained submerged. Most importantly, the Nautilus was fitted with three ice drills, allowing the submarine to recharge batteries, refresh air and even allow the crew to exit while the submarine still remained below the ice. 

The Nautilus and her crew of 20 men began their expedition to the North Pole in June of 1931. 
None of them realized how grueling their journey would be, and almost immediately things began to go wrong.

snippet.description:
Carin León - Cuando La Vida Sea Trago [Official Video]

🦁 Suscríbete a mi canal: 
https://n9.cl/kp49a

Escucha "Cuando La Vida Sea Trago" en tu plataforma favorita: 
https://carinleon.lnk.to/CuandoLaVidaSeaTrago

LETRA👇:

Soy el que le sacó canas a mamá
El que siempre soñó con tener lana
Y desde una edad temprana
Siempre tuve esa ambición

Yo soy el dolor de cabeza de las suegras
De la familia soy la oveja negra
De chamaco siempre di problemas y preocupación

Un grosero pero tuve educación
A la escuela sólo iba por la linda del salón
Hubo una que me falló
Desde ahí soy un cabrón
Solamente porque mami me enseñó a pedir perdón

Y que me disculpe la que ofendí por salir mujeriego 
Desde morro me gustó el desmadre
Así soy, no lo niego
Y el que tiene derecho a juzgarme
Lo veo después en el cementerio
Mientras tanto, cuando la vida sea trago
Me la tomo en serio

No vine a ser ejemplo a seguir
Yo soy como soy
Mami quería un buen hombre
Y le salió un bad boy
No me quieran cambiar
Yo estoy bien como estoy
Les duele porque gusto no les doy

No ha llegado una que me enderece
Una se va y me escriben trece
Portarme bien no está en mis intereses
Pico y me voy, después me lo agradeces

Soy bien loco y en eso tienen razón
Puedo querer a muchas, tengo grande el corazón
Agradezco la intención, pero no tengo solución
Y solamente porque mami me enseñó a pedir perdón

Y que me disculpe la que ofendí por salir mujeriego 
Desde morro me gustó el desmadre
Así soy, no lo niego
Y el que tiene derecho a juzgarme
Lo veo después en el cementerio
Mientras tanto, cuando la vida sea trago
Me la tomo en serio

snippet.title: Zach Bryan - 28
snippet.description:
You took a train to the south side of Boston,
You showed me where your old man stayed,
Took 28 years of blood I was lost in,
To feel loved on my own birthday,
I always felt like I’s in between something,
Like home and somewhere far away,
But tonight on the west side in a bar out in Brooklyn,
I saw tears outline your face,

How lucky are we?
It’s been a hell of a week, but we’re all grown now,
There’s smoke seeping out, of your bloody teeth,
But you’re home somehow,

I’ll be upstairs with the guitar I’s given,
When I was barley fourteen,
When did McGlinchey’s get so damn crowded,
And why are the crowds so damn green?
I lost my mind on the streets of the city,
Maybe I lost all hope too,
Took 28 years of blood pumping through me,
To get to this evening with you,

How lucky are we?
It’s been a hell of a week, but we’re all grown now,
There’s smoke seeping out, of your bloody teeth,
But you’re home somehow,

How lucky are we?
It’s been a hell of a week, but we’re all grown now,
There’s smoke seeping out, of your bloody teeth,
But you’re home somehow

snippet.title: Tiger Woods Second Round | Every Single Shot | The Masters
snippet.description:
Every shot from Tiger Woods' second-round 72. #themasters

Since 1934, the Masters Tournament has been home to some of golf’s greatest moments. Amidst blooming azaleas, towering pines and flowering dogwoods, the first full week of April ushers in a stage unique to golf and to sport. Over four days and 72 holes, the smallest field in major championship golf competes for a chance to capture the Green Jacket and a place in Masters history.

snippet.title: Zach Bryan - Like Ida
snippet.description:
When you wake in the morning and I’m not by your side,
just know that I’m halfway to Dallas,
I’m stoned out my mind, I’m half buzzed ‘bout full time since you left me to die here last August,
When you make it to Nashville, you can tell by one hat tilt, that that shit just ain’t my scene,
I like out of tune guitars, taking jokes too far and my bartenders extra damn mean, 

So roll where you’re rolling,
I’ll be praying you’re fine,
Wherever you’re going,
Stay walking that line,
‘Cause they’ll eat and they’ll spit ya’,
But you’re not their fool,
They don’t know ya’ like ida,
Back home on barstools,

I’m out on the road, when I’m going I go,
I make music with all of my friends,
I miss your silhouette, catching coastal sunsets,
And the sound of that rusty door hinge,
But that days bound to come when I finish this run,
And I’m rolling right into your arms,
And that bullshit you see on the late night TV
is a long way from our beating hearts, 

So roll where you’re rolling,
I’ll be praying you’re fine,
Go where you’re going,
Stay walking that line,
‘Cause they’ll eat and they’ll spit ya’,
But you ain’t their fool,
They don’t know ya’ like ida,
Back home on barstools,

So roll where you’re rolling,
I’ll be praying you’re fine,
Wherever you’re going,
Stay walking that line,
‘Cause they’ll eat and they’ll spit ya’,
But you ain’t their fool,
They don’t know ya’ like ida,
Back home on barstools

Best guitarist of all time, member of the band: Chris Braun

snippet.title: Season 10: Venture Forth | Overwatch 2 Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Overwatch 2  Season 10: Venture Forth launches April 16!

Unlock our new Damage Hero, Venture. Dig into their ability kit and explore new underground mechanics.

Venture and all other Heroes are unlocked immediately for everyone who has completed the new player experience. Venture will also be available in Competitive at launch.

Blur the lines between good and evil with the Mirrorwatch Event, where the virtuous have crumbled into villainy, and the wicked emerge as heroes.

Collect Mythic Prisms as you progress through the Battle Pass and use them to unlock Vengeance Mercy and select previous skins at the Mythic Shop!

Engage in an intense tug of war as you vie for control across a series of capture points in Clash Game Mode Trial, an exciting new 5v5 game mode.

Overwatch 2 is free to play for everyone on console & PC!

_

snippet.description:
Every single shot from Bryson DeChambeau's first round. #themasters 

---

Since 1934, the Masters Tournament has been home to some of golf’s greatest moments. Amidst blooming azaleas, towering pines and flowering dogwoods, the first full week of April ushers in a stage unique to golf and to sport. Over four days and 72 holes, the smallest field in major championship golf competes for a chance to capture the Green Jacket and a place in Masters history.

snippet.title: Dark Matter — Official Trailer | Apple TV+
snippet.description:
There are infinite realities. This is the one where Jason Dessen kidnaps himself. Based on the New York Times bestseller, Dark Matter premieres May 8. https://apple.co/_DarkMatter

Dark Matter is a sci-fi thriller series based on the blockbuster book by acclaimed, bestselling author Blake Crouch. The nine-episode series features an ensemble cast that includes Joel Edgerton, Jennifer Connelly, Alice Braga, Jimmi Simpson, Dayo Okeniyi and Oakes Fegley. Dark Matter makes its global debut on Apple TV+ on May 8, 2024, premiering with the first two episodes, followed by new episodes every Wednesday through June 26.

Hailed as one of the best sci-fi novels of the decade, Dark Matter is a story about the road not taken. The series will follow Jason Dessen (played by Joel Edgerton), a physicist, professor and family man who — one night while walking home on the streets of Chicago — is abducted into an alternate version of his life. Wonder quickly turns to nightmare when he tries to return to his reality amid the mind-bending landscape of lives he could have lived. In this labyrinth of realities, he embarks on a harrowing journey to get back to his true family and save them from the most terrifying, unbeatable foe imaginable: himself.

Crouch serves as executive producer, showrunner, and writer alongside executive producers Matt Tolmach and David Manpearl for Matt Tolmach Productions, and Joel Edgerton. Dark Matter is produced for Apple TV+ by Sony Pictures Television. 

Song: “I Can Never Go Home Anymore” by The Shangri-Las https://music.apple.com/us/album/i-can-never-go-home-anymore/1443845929?i=1443846815

snippet.title: Young Woman and the Sea | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
21 miles and a nice day for a swim. Experience the incredible true story of #YoungWomanAndTheSea, in select theaters May 31.

Disney’s “Young Woman and the Sea,” the extraordinary true story of Trudy Ederle, the first woman to successfully swim the English Channel, is coming to theaters nationwide in a special engagement May 31, 2024.
 
Daisy Ridley stars as the accomplished swimmer who was born to immigrant parents in New York City in 1905. Through the steadfast support of her older sister and supportive trainers, she overcame adversity and the animosity of a patriarchal society to rise through the ranks of the Olympic swimming team and complete the staggering achievement – a 21-mile trek from France to England. “Young Woman and the Sea,” which also stars Tilda Cobham-Hervey, Stephen Graham, Kim Bodnia, Christopher Eccleston, and Glenn Fleshler, is directed by Joachim Rønning and written by Jeff Nathanson, based on the book “Young Woman and the Sea: How Trudy Ederle Conquered the English Channel and Inspired the World” by Glenn Stout. The producers are Jerry Bruckheimer, Chad Oman, and Jeff Nathanson, with John G. Scotti, Daisy Ridley, and Joachim Rønning serving as executive producers.
 
“Young Woman and the Sea” will open in select theaters May 31, 2024.

What happened to DOGDAY?!
Dogday is one of the Smiling Critters from Poppy Playtime Chapter 3: Deep Sleep (created by Mob Entertainment). He’s a giant toy dog who was captured by Catnap and imprisoned in a jail cell… and his legs were tragically ripped off. His design and scene in the game is pretty creepy and insane, so after making our DIY animatronic Catnap, we knew a hanging Dog Day animatronic had to be next.

We started by making some fake walls in the style of theatrical flats to act as his jail cell. His frame was made of steel and powered by pneumatics, thanks to the help of Hallucinations Creations who make amazing pneumatic animatronic mechs for the haunted house industry. We used wire, duct tape, and foam to make the shape of his body and covered the whole thing in shaggy fur. His head was custom 3D modeled and 3D printed. The whole thing was animated with a prop controller from Purgatory Props.

We love how our real life DogDay turned out! He’s an awesome pneumatic prop and he's going to make the perfect companion to our growing collection of custom Halloween animatronics like our Catnap, Huggy Wuggy and Springtrap animatronics. Who do you want to see us make next? And where do we put this giant prop now?!

Thanks for watching and Stay Wicked, y’all!

#DogDay
#PoppyPlaytime
#Animatronics

Jaimie and Jay make a real life DogDay from Poppy Playtime! -- Go to https://dayoneapp.com/wickedmakers and use code: wickedmakers to get a limited-time offer of a two-month free trial with Day One Journal Premium!

SUBSCRIBE ► http://bit.ly/2EypcHI

DogDay 3D Printing Files (and more): ► https://patreon.com/wickedmakers
Wicked Makers T-Shirts & Merch! ► https://shopwickedmakers.com/

Special Thanks to:
Hallucinations Creations ► http://hallucinationscreations.com/
Purgatory Props ► https://purgatoryprops.com/
DogDay Sculpt by Beardless Props ► https://instagram.com/beardless.props/

Join our Community on Discord & Facebook ►
https://discord.gg/wickedmakers
https://www.facebook.com/groups/439135431429446

Our Favorite 3D Printer ► https://shrsl.com/4a3kf
Our Favorite 3D Printing Filament ► https://collabs.shop/llx8l1

MATERIALS & TOOLS WE USED ►

EVA Foam: https://amzn.to/3wGNPRP

Big Zipper: https://amzn.to/3ToKVdq

Orange, Brown, and Yellow Fur Blankets: 
Duct Tape: https://amzn.to/3T3wH0a
Mod Podge: https://amzn.to/4c5PZL8
Contact Cement: https://amzn.to/3T1PKI9
Spot Putty - https://amzn.to/3vtzc3N
Clear Fillable Christmas Ornaments - https://amzn.to/3Snjqk1
Super Glue - https://amzn.to/48OIBkQ
Hot Glue Gun: https://amzn.to/4c2MiWb
Heat Gun: https://amzn.to/43350co
Fabric Scissors

OUR CAMERA/FILMING GEAR ►
Our Main Camera: https://amzn.to/3PEaILC
Secondary Camera: https://amzn.to/46jDrfF (or iPhone)
Microphones: https://amzn.to/3rBM5XO
Most Used Lens: https://amzn.to/3LMWhng
Main Tripod: https://amzn.to/46q8WV4
Light #1: https://amzn.to/3Q0lVX5
Light #2 (cheaper): https://amzn.to/3PJzBp0
C-Stands: https://amzn.to/3LMamB8
Colored Lights (mounted): https://amzn.to/3PEKfgS
Colored Lights (handheld): https://amzn.to/3F1fJc3
Softbox: https://amzn.to/46zLTal
Softbox Lantern: https://amzn.to/46wtJ9x
Gimbal: https://amzn.to/3ZHgNv5
Camera Bag (for travel): https://amzn.to/46cHdY1

What happened to DOGDAY?!
Dogday is one of the Smiling Critters from Poppy Playtime Chapter 3: Deep Sleep (created by Mob Entertainment). He’s a giant toy dog who was captured by Catnap and imprisoned in a jail cell… and his legs were tragically ripped off. His design and scene in the game is pretty creepy and insane, so after making our DIY animatronic Catnap, we knew a hanging Dog Day animatronic had to be next.

We started by making some fake walls in the style of theatrical flats to act as his jail cell. His frame was made of steel and powered by pneumatics, thanks to the help of Hallucinations Creations who make amazing pneumatic animatronic mechs for the haunted house industry. We used wire, duct tape, and foam to make the shape of his body and covered the whole thing in shaggy fur. His head was custom 3D modeled and 3D printed. The whole thing was animated with a prop controller from Purgatory Props.

We love how our real life DogDay turned out! He’s an awesome pneumatic prop and he's going to make the perfect companion to our growing collection of custom Halloween animatronics like our Catnap, Huggy Wuggy and Springtrap animatronics. Who do you want to see us make next? And where do we put this giant prop now?!

Thanks for watching and Stay Wicked, y’all!

snippet.title: Shannon Sharpe goes off on Russell Wilson for saying he "opened doors" for Black QBs | Nightcap
snippet.description:
Shannon Sharpe and Chad "Ochocinco" Johnson react to Russell Wilson's latest comments about opening doors for current black quarterbacks. Unc says Warren Moon, Doug Williams, Michael Vick, and other great black QBs opened the door for Russ and should be given credit for their contributions to the NFL.

Shannon Sharpe and Chad "Ochocinco" Johnson react to Russell Wilson's latest comments about opening doors for current black quarterbacks. Unc says Warren Moon, Doug Williams, Michael Vick, and other great black QBs opened the door for Russ and should be given credit for their contributions to the NFL.

Follow Nightcap on all platforms: 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/NightcapShow_
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/nightcapshow_/
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@nightcapshow_
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61551822396133

ABOUT NIGHTCAP: 
No more waiting until morning. Nightcap is the new nighttime sports talk destination with legends Shannon Sharpe, Chad “Ochocinco” Johnson, and Gilbert Arenas. Hang out with Unc, Ocho, and Gil as they give their unfiltered takes on the latest headlines from the NFL, NBA, and college football, and give their instant reactions to the biggest games moments after they end.

snippet.title: Speak No Evil | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
See no evil. Hear no evil.
#SpeakNoEvilMovie only in theaters September 13.  

-----

When an American family is invited to spend the weekend at the idyllic country estate of a charming British family they befriended on vacation, what begins as a dream holiday soon warps into a snarled psychological nightmare. 

From Blumhouse, the producer of The Black Phone, Get Out and The Invisible Man, comes an intense suspense thriller for our modern age, starring BAFTA award-winner James McAvoy (Split, Glass) in a riveting performance as the charismatic, alpha-male estate owner whose untrammeled hospitality masks an unspeakable darkness. 

Speak No Evil stars Mackenzie Davis (Terminator: Dark Fate, Halt and Catch Fire) and SAG award-winner Scoot McNairy (Argo, A Quiet Place Part II) as American couple Louise and Ben Dalton, who, along with their 11-year-old daughter Agnes (Alix West Lefler; The Good Nurse, Riverdale), accept the weekend-holiday invitation of Paddy (McAvoy), his wife Ciara (Aisling Franciosi; Game of Thrones, The Fall) and their furtive, mute son Ant (newcomer Daniel Hough).

Written for the screen and directed by James Watkins, the writer-director of Eden Lake and the award-winning gothic ghost story The Woman in Black, Speak No Evil is based on the screenplay of the 2022 Danish horror sensation Gæsterne, written by Christian Tafdrup and Mads Tafdrup. That film earned 11 Danish Film Awards nominations, the Danish equivalent of the Oscars. 

Speak No Evil is produced by Jason Blum (Five Nights at Freddy’s, M3GAN) for Blumhouse and by Paul Ritchie (McMafia, The Ipcress File) and is executive produced by Beatriz Sequeira for Blumhouse, Jacob Jarek and Christian Tafdrup. 


Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/speaknoevilthefilm   
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/speaknoevilthemovie/
X: https://twitter.com/speaknoevil24
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@universalpics 
Website: https://www.speaknoevilmovie.com/

snippet.title: JOJO SIWA: The Woman Behind The Bow
snippet.description:
Watch the full episode on Spotify - it's live right now! https://bit.ly/CallHerDaddy

Join Alex in the studio for a sit-down interview with JoJo Siwa. JoJo hits the ground running with a major life update… her parents have officially moved out! The two discuss being independent for the first time and how JoJo navigated having multiple partners live at home with her entire family. JoJo opens up about child stardom, her experience on Dance Moms, how she truly felt about the bullying on set, and how shouldering all that financial pressure at such a young age impacted her. JoJo then gushes about how she wants to have her own kids one day (Freddy, Eddy, and Teddy) while Alex tries to talk her out of giving her kids rhyming names. The two discuss JoJo’s bow era and Alex asks the questions we’ve ALL been wondering. JoJo talks about the extreme amount of internet hate she’s recently gotten and how she handles it. Alex asks JoJo all about her current dating life, why she makes potential partners go through a background check, and what she’s looking for now. Finally, the two discuss JoJo’s new look, music, and stepping into her adult era. Enjoy!

snippet.title: Star Wars Outlaws: Official Story Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming August 30th, 2024. Play up to 3 days early with Gold or Ultimate edition, which includes the base game and season pass.
 
Pre-order now and receive the Kessel Runner Bonus Pack including cosmetics for your speeder and The Trailblazer starship!*
 
With the pre-order bonus, receive the Kessel Runner Bonus Pack* including: 
- A cosmetic pack for your speeder.
- A cosmetic for your starship, The Trailblazer.
 
*Offer, content, and dates subject to change. Content may be available for purchase and/or as giveaway(s) separately at Ubisoft’s sole discretion at any time.

About Star Wars Outlaws:
Experience the first-ever open world Star Wars™ game, set between the events ofThe Empire Strikes Back and Return of the Jedi. Explore distinct planets across the galaxy, both iconic and new. Risk it all as Kay Vess, an emerging scoundrel seeking freedom and the means to start a new life, along with her companion Nix. Fight, steal, and outwit your way through the galaxy’s crime syndicates as you join the galaxy’s most wanted.

Learn more at: https://starwarsoutlaws.com/

INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/starwarsoutlaws/
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/starwarsoutlaws
DISCORD: https://discord.gg/starwarsoutlaws

About Ubisoft:
Ubisoft is a creator of worlds, committed to enriching players’ lives with original and memorable entertainment experiences. Ubisoft’s global teams create and develop a deep and diverse portfolio of games, featuring brands such as Assassin’s Creed®, Brawlhalla®, For Honor®, Far Cry®, Tom Clancy’s Ghost Recon®, Just Dance®, Rabbids®, Tom Clancy’s Rainbow Six®, The Crew®, Tom Clancy’s The Division®, and Watch Dogs®. Through Ubisoft Connect, players can enjoy an ecosystem of services to enhance their gaming experience, get rewards and connect with friends across platforms. With Ubisoft+, the subscription service, they can access a growing catalog of more than 100 Ubisoft games and DLC. For the 2021–22 fiscal year, Ubisoft generated net bookings of €2,129 million. To learn more, please visit: www.ubisoftgroup.com.

pt-BR.description:
Chegando em 30 de agosto de 2024. Jogue com até 3 dias de antecedência com as Edições Gold ou Ultimate, que incluem o jogo base e o passe de temporada.
 
Reserve o jogo agora e receba o Pacote Bônus Contrabandistas de Kessel, incluindo cosméticos para seu speeder e a espaçonave Trailblazer!*
 
Com o bônus de pré-venda, receba o Pacote Bônus Contrabandistas de Kessel, incluindo: 
- Um pacote cosmético para seu speeder.
- Um cosmético para a sua espaçonave, a Trailblazer.
 
*Oferta, conteúdo e datas sujeitos a mudança. O conteúdo pode estar disponível para compra e/ou como distribuição(ões) separadamente a critério único da Ubisoft a qualquer momento.

Star Wars Outlaws:
Vivencie o primeiro jogo de mundo aberto de Star Wars™ — ambientado entre os eventos de O Império Contra-Ataca e O Retorno de Jedi — e explore planetas novos e lendários por toda a galáxia. Aposte tudo na pele de Kay Vess, uma vigarista em ascensão que busca liberdade e meios para começar uma nova vida, com seu parceiro Nix. Lute, roube e trapaceie em meio aos sindicatos do crime e entre para o rol dos mais procurados da galáxia.

A galáxia está cheia de oportunidades para quem tem coragem de arriscar.

Saiba mais em: https://starwarsoutlaws.com/

INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/starwarsoutlaws/
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/starwarsoutlaws

Sobre a Ubisoft:
A Ubisoft é uma criadora de mundos, comprometida em enriquecer a vida dos jogadores com experiências de entretenimento originais e memoráveis. As equipes globais da Ubisoft criam e desenvolvem um portfólio profundo e diversificado de jogos, com marcas como Assassin's Creed®, Brawlhalla®, For Honor®, Far Cry®, Tom Clancy's Ghost Recon®, Just Dance®, Rabbids®, Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six ®, The Crew®, Tom Clancy's The Division® e Watch Dogs®. Por meio da Ubisoft Connect, os jogadores podem desfrutar de um ecossistema de serviços para aprimorar sua experiência de jogo, obter recompensas e se conectar com amigos em todas as plataformas. Com o Ubisoft+, o serviço de assinatura, eles podem acessar um catálogo crescente de mais de 100 jogos e DLCs da Ubisoft. Para o ano fiscal de 2021-22, a Ubisoft gerou reservas líquidas de € 2,129 milhões. Para saber mais, visite: www.ubisoftgroup.com.

fr.title: Star Wars Outlaws: Bande-annonce officielle de l'histoire
fr.description:
Disponible le 30 août 2024. Jouez jusqu'à 3 jours plus tôt avec la Gold Edition ou l'Ultimate Edition, qui comprennent le jeu de base et le pass saisonnier.
 
Précommandez maintenant pour recevoir le pack bonus Raid de Kessel, qui contient des éléments esthétiques pour votre speeder et votre vaisseau, le Trailblazer !*
 
Précommandez le jeu et recevez le pack bonus Raid de Kessel*, qui contient : 
- Un ensemble d'éléments esthétiques pour votre speeder.
- Un ensemble d'éléments esthétiques pour votre vaisseau, le Trailblazer.

À propos de Star Wars Outlaws :
Découvrez le tout premier jeu Star Wars™ en monde ouvert se déroulant entre les événements de L'Empire contre-attaque et du Retour du Jedi. Explorez des planètes variées, célèbres et inconnues, à travers la galaxie. Risquez le tout pour le tout en incarnant Kay Vess, une vaurienne en pleine ascension recherchant liberté et moyens de commencer une nouvelle vie aux côtés de son compagnon, Nix. Combattez, volez et gardez une longueur d'avance sur les syndicats du crime en rejoignant les hors-la-loi les plus recherchés de l'univers.

La galaxie regorge d'opportunités pour qui est prêt à prendre des risques.

Bestelle jetzt vor und erhalte das Bonuspaket „Kesselflieger“, mit kosmetischen Gegenständen für deinen Gleiter und dein Raumschiff, die Bahnbrecher!*
 
Mit dem Vorbesteller-Bonus erhältst du das Bonuspaket „Kesselflieger“, es enthält: 
- Ein kosmetisches Paket für deinen Gleiter.
- Einen kosmetischen Gegenstand für dein Raumschiff, die Bahnbrecher

Über Star Wars Outlaws:
Erlebe das erste Open-World-Spiel im Star Wars™ -Universum; mit einer Geschichte, die zwischen den Ereignissen von Das Imperium Schlägt zurück und Die Rückkehr der Jedi-Ritter angesiedelt ist. Erkunde neue und bekannte Planeten in der gesamten Galaxie. Du bist Kay Vess, eine Gesetzlose, die zusammen mit ihrem Gefährten Nix alles riskiert, um die Freiheit zu erlangen und ein neues Leben zu beginnen. Kämpfe, klaue und trickse dich durch die Verbrechersyndikate und werde zu einer der meistgesuchten Personen der Galaxie.

Wenn du bereit bist, Risiken einzugehen, bietet die Galaxie endlose Möglichkeiten.

pl.title: Star Wars Outlaws: Oficjalny zwiastun fabularny
pl.description:
Premiera 30 sierpnia 2024 Zagraj nawet 3 dni wcześniej dzięki wydaniu Gold lub Ultimate Edition z podstawową wersją gry i przepustką sezonową.
 
Zamów w przedsprzedaży i otrzymaj pakiet dodatkowy „Przemytniczka z Kessel”, a w nim przedmioty kosmetyczne do ścigacza i statku kosmicznego – Śmiałka!*
 
W ramach premii przedsprzedażowej otrzymasz pakiet dodatkowy „Przemytniczka z Kessel”* zawierający:
– zestaw elementów kosmetycznych do ścigacza,
– element kosmetyczny dla twojego statku kosmicznego – Śmiałka.
 
*Oferta, jej zawartość oraz daty mogą ulec zmianom. Zawartość może w dowolnym momencie pojawić się w sprzedaży i/lub w ramach darmowych nagród zgodnie z wyłączną decyzją firmy Ubisoft.

O grze Star Wars Outlaws:
Poznaj pierwszą w historii grę z uniwersum Star Wars™ z otwartym światem, umiejscowioną pomiędzy wydarzeniami z filmów „Imperium Kontratakuje” oraz „Powrót Jedi”. Odkrywaj niezwykłe planety w całej galaktyce, zarówno te ikoniczne, jak i zupełnie nowe. Postaw wszystko na jedną kartę jako Kay Vess – zyskująca reputację łotrzyca, która pragnie rozpocząć nowe życie jako wolna osoba. Razem ze swoim towarzyszem Nixem walcz, kradnij i przechytrz najpotężniejsze syndykaty przestępcze, by dołączyć do najbardziej poszukiwanych osób w galaktyce.

Jeśli nie boisz się ryzyka, galaktyka jest pełna możliwości.

2024年8月30日发布购买黄金版或终极版可最快提前三天体验游戏，包括游戏本体与季票。

现在预购，即可获得“科舍尔走私犯”奖励包，内含飞行摩托和星舰“开拓者号”的外观！*

预购即可获得“科舍尔走私犯”奖励包*预购奖励，内含：

关于《星球大战：亡命徒》：
进入有史以来第一部开放世界《星球大战》游戏，体验发生在《帝国反击战》和《绝地归来》之间的全新故事。银河系中诸多或是经典，或是全新的星球等待着你的探索。你将扮演凯·维斯——一名刚刚崭露头角的恶棍——并与好搭档尼克斯一起，在凶险的宇宙中寻求自由，设法开启全新的生活。你可以通过战斗、偷窃或是智取，在银河系当中的各大犯罪集团间自由周旋，并登上银河帝国系的最高通缉名单。

只要你敢于冒险，银河系遍地都是机遇。

Reserva el juego ya y recibe el paquete de bonificación Corredora de Kessel, que incluye objetos cosméticos para tu speeder y para tu nave estelar, la Cazaestelas.*

Experimenta el primer juego de mundo abierto de Star Wars™, ambientado entre los acontecimientos de El Imperio contraataca y El retorno del Jedi, y explora planetas únicos por toda la galaxia, tanto nuevos como clásicos. Arriésgalo todo encarnando a Kay Vess, una buscavidas novata que busca la libertad y la manera de comenzar una nueva vida junto con Nix, su compañero de viaje. Lucha, roba y engaña a los sindicatos del crimen de toda la galaxia y únete a la lista de los más buscados.

Özgürlüğünün peşinde koşan ve yeni bir hayata başlamanın yollarını arayan, yükselen bir kurumsak olan Kay Vess ve yoldaşı Nix ile tüm riskleri göze alın. ko.title: 스타워즈: 아웃로: 공식 스토리 트레일러
ko.description:
2024년 8월 30일에 출시됩니다. 게임 본편과 시즌 패스가 들어있는 골드 또는 얼티밋 에디션으로 최대 3일 먼저 플레이해 보세요.
 
지금 바로 예약 구매하고 스피더와 트레일블레이저 우주선을 위한 외형 아이템이 포함된 케셀 러너 보너스 팩을 획득하세요!*
 
예약 구매 보너스를 통해 케셀 러너 보너스 팩*의 구성품을 획득하세요. 
- 스피더를 위한 외형 아이템 팩
- 트레일블레이저 우주선을 위한 외형 아이템
  
*상품, 콘텐츠, 일정은 추후 변경될 수 있습니다. 콘텐츠는 언제든 유비소프트의 재량에 따라 판매 상품 및/또는 경품으로 별도 제공될 수 있습니다.

Star Wars Outlaws 개요:
'제국의 역습'과 '제다이의 귀환' 사이의 이야기를 다룬 세계 최초의 오픈 월드 스타워즈 게임을 즐겨보세요! 은하계의 여러 행성을 탐험하세요. 널리 알려진 상징적인 행성과 새로운 행성을 모두 만나볼 수 있습니다. 자유, 그리고 새로운 삶을 시작하기 위한 수단을 찾고 있는 악당 '케이 베스'로 동료 '닉스'와 함께 무모한 모험을 떠나세요. 여러분은 싸우고, 훔치고, 은하계 범죄 조직들 틈에서 입지를 다지면서 악명 높은 지명 수배자로 거듭납니다.

위험을 감수할 각오만 되어있다면, 은하계는 다양한 기회로 가득 차 있습니다.

th.description:
มาวันที่ 30 สิงหาคม 2024 เล่นล่วงหน้าก่อนใคร 3 วันด้วยโกลด์หรืออัลติเมทอิดิชั่น ซึ่งประกอบด้วยตัวเกมหลักและซีซั่นพาส
 
สั่งซื้อล่วงหน้าตอนนี้และรับแพ็กโบนัสเคสเซลรันเนอร์ รวมถึงของตกแต่งสำหรับยานสปีดเดอร์และยานอวกาศเทรลเบลเซอร์ไปได้เลย!*
 
หากสั่งซื้อล่วงหน้า จะได้รับแพ็กโบนัสเคสเซลรันเนอร์* ซึ่งประกอบด้วย: 
- แพ็กของตกแต่งสำหรับยานสปีดเดอร์
- ของตกแต่งสำหรับยานอวกาศเทรลเบลเซอร์
  
*ข้อเสนอ เนื้อหา และวันที่อาจมีการเปลี่ยนแปลง เนื้อหาอาจมีให้ซื้อและ/หรือเป็นของขวัญแจกแยกกันตามดุลยพินิจของ Ubisoft แต่เพียงผู้เดียวได้ตลอดเวลา

เกี่ยวกับ Star Wars Outlaws:
สัมผัสประสบการณ์เกม Star Wars™ แบบโอเพนเวิร์ลเกมแรก เกิดขึ้นช่วงเหตุการณ์ The Empire Strikes Back และ Return of the Jedi สำรวจดวงดาวที่หลากหลายทั่วกาแล็กซีซึ่งมีทั้งความโดดเด่นและความแปลกใหม่ ทุ่มสุดตัวในฐานะ เคย์ เวส วายร้ายหน้าใหม่ผู้ออกแสวงหาอิสรภาพและหนทางในการเริ่มต้นชีวิตใหม่พร้อมกับนิกซ์คู่หูของเธอ ต่อสู้ ช่วงชิง และชิงไหวพริบในแบบของตนเองไปกับกลุ่มอาชญากรกาแล็กซีเมื่อคุณเข้าร่วมกับกลุ่มผู้ที่กาแล็กซีที่ต้องการตัวมากที่สุด

หากคุณยอมเสี่ยง คุณจะได้พบกับโอกาสมากมายที่กาแล็กซีนี้รอมอบให้แน่นอน

เรียนรู้เพิ่มเติมที่: https://starwarsoutlaws.com/

INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/starwarsoutlaws/
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/starwarsoutlaws
DISCORD: https://discord.gg/starwarsoutlaws

เกี่ยวกับ Ubisoft
Ubisoft คือผู้สร้างสรรค์, มุ่งมั่นที่จะเติมเต็มชีวิตของผู้เล่นด้วยประสบการณ์ความบันเทิงที่เป็นต้นฉบับและน่าจดจำ ทีมงานระดับโลกของ Ubisoft ได้สร้างและพัฒนาผลงานเกมที่ลึกซึ้งและหลากหลาย โดยมีแบรนด์ต่าง ๆ อาทิ Assassin's Creed ®, Brawlhalla®, For Honor®, Far Cry®, Tom Clancy's Ghost Recon®, Just Dance®, Rabbids, Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six®, The Crew®, Tom Clancy's The Division® และ Watch Dogs® ผู้เล่นสามารถเพลิดเพลินกับระบบนิเวศการบริการที่รองรับตัวเกม เพื่อยกระดับประสบการณ์การเล่น รับรางวัล และเชื่อมต่อกับเพื่อนฝูง ผ่านแพลตฟอร์ม Ubisoft Connect ด้วยบริการสมัครสมาชิก Ubisoft+ พวกเขาสามารถเข้าถึงแคตตาล็อกเกมและ DLC ของ Ubisoft ที่ยังคงเพิ่มขึ้นอย่างต่อเนื่องมากกว่า 100 เกม สำหรับปีงบประมาณ 2564-2565 Ubisoft มีรายได้ทางบัญชีสุทธิที่ 2,129 ล้านยูโร หากต้องการเรียนรู้เพิ่มเติม โปรดไปที่: www.ubisoftgroup.com

zh-Hant.title: 官方劇情預告片 - 星際大戰：亡命之徒
zh-Hant.description:
將於 2024 年 8 月 30 日推出。透過黃金版或終極版提早最多 3 天搶先遊玩遊戲，內含主遊戲與季票。

立即預購以取得「凱瑟航道旅者」好禮組合包，內含適用於飛行器與「拓荒者號」星際飛船的造型！*

預購禮包含「凱瑟航道旅者」好禮組合包*，內容有：
- 適用於飛行器的造型組合包。
- 適用於「拓荒者號」星際飛船的造型。

*特惠、內容與日期有變動之可能。Ubisoft 可隨時全權決定此內容是否開放購買及／或單獨作為贈品送出。

關於《Star Wars Outlaws》：
體驗《Star Wars》首次的開放式世界玩法，故事設定在《帝國大反擊》以及《絕地大反攻》之間。探索銀河系獨具特色的星球，包括耳熟能詳的地點與全新星球。你將扮演凱．維斯，這名異軍突起的無賴痞子在夥伴小尼的陪伴下，賭上一切來追逐自由並重獲新生。靠著戰鬥、偷竊、以及與各個犯罪集團周旋，晉身成為銀河系最高通緝的大人物。

只要你願意承擔風險，銀河系處處充滿了良機。

前往官網了解詳情：https://starwarsoutlaws.com/

INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/starwarsoutlaws/
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/starwarsoutlaws
DISCORD: https://discord.gg/starwarsoutlaws

關於 Ubisoft：
Ubisoft 是開發、發行與經銷互動式娛樂遊戲與服務的領導廠商，旗下擁有豐富多元的全球知名品牌，包括《刺客教條》、《英靈神殿大亂鬥》、《極地戰嚎》、《榮耀戰魂》、《Just Dance 舞力全開》、《看門狗》、《瘋狂兔子》，以及包含《火線獵殺》、《虹彩六號》和《全境封鎖》的《湯姆克蘭西》電玩遊戲系列。透過 Ubisoft Connect，玩家可享用豐富且完整的服務以提升遊戲體驗、獲得獎勵和與不同平台上的好友互動。訂閱 Ubisoft+ 服務，玩家甚至可以暢玩超過 100 款 Ubisoft 遊戲及擴充內容。Ubisoft 遍及全球各地的開發工作室與辦事處團隊致力於在包含家用遊樂器主機、行動裝置、平板電腦和 PC 等所有熱門遊戲平台上，提供玩家富有原創性且令人回味無窮的遊戲體驗。2021-22 會計年度 Ubisoft 的預定淨收入為 21 億 2 千 9 百萬歐元。如欲取得更進一步資訊，請造訪 www.ubisoftgroup.com/。

it.title: Star Wars Outlaws: Trailer ufficiale della storia
it.description:
Disponibile il 30 agosto 2024 Gioca fino a 3 giorni prima grazie alla Gold o alla Ultimate Edition, che include il gioco base e il Season Pass.
 
Preordina ora e riceverai il pacchetto bonus Pilota di Kessel, che include contenuti estetici per lo speeder e l'astronave Trailblazer!*
 
Con il bonus per il preordine riceverai il pacchetto bonus Pilota di Kessel*, che include: 
- Un pacchetto estetico per il tuo speeder.
- Un contenuto estetico per la tua astronave, la Trailblazer

Star Wars Outlaws:
Scopri il primissimo gioco open world di Star Wars™, ambientato fra gli eventi de L'Impero colpisce ancora e Il ritorno dello Jedi. Esplora pianeti di ogni tipo in tutta la galassia, alcuni iconici e altri mai visti prima. Rischia tutto nei panni di Kay Vess, una giovane canaglia in cerca di libertà e dei mezzi per cominciare una nuova vita, al fianco del suo compagno Nix. Combatti, ruba e gioca d'astuzia per fare carriera nel mondo del crimine ed entrare nell'elenco dei più temuti ricercati della galassia.

La galassia è ricca di opportunità... per chi è disposto a rischiare.


Scopri di più su: https://starwarsoutlaws.com/

INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/starwarsoutlaws/
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/starwarsoutlaws
DISCORD: https://discord.gg/starwarsoutlaws

Informazioni su Ubisoft: 
Ubisoft è creatore di mondi, si dedica ad arricchire la vita dei giocatori con esperienze di gioco originali e memorabili. I suoi team in tutto il mondo creano e sviluppano un diversificato portfolio di giochi che comprendono marchi come Assassin’s Creed®, Brawlhalla®, For Honor®, Far Cry®, Tom Clancy’s Ghost Recon®, Just Dance®, Rabbids, Tom Clancy’s Rainbow Six®, The Crew®, Tom Clancy’s The Division® e Watch Dogs®. Tramite Ubisoft Connect, i giocatori possono sperimentare un ecosistema di servizi per migliorare la propria esperienza di gioco, ottenere ricompense e connettersi con amici attraverso differenti piattaforme. Con Ubisoft+, il servizio di abbonamento di Ubisoft, possono accedere a un crescente catalogo di più di 100 giochi Ubisoft e DLC. Per l’anno fiscale 2021-22 Ubisoft ha realizzato un fatturato di 2.129 milioni di euro. Per maggiori informazioni consulta il sito: www.ubisoftgroup.com.  ©2022 Ubisoft Entertainment. ar.title: إعلان القصة الترويجي الرسمي : Star Wars Outlaws
ar.description:
تصدر في 30 أغسطس 2024 يمكنكم اللعب مبكراً بما يصل إلى 3 أيام مع الإصدار الذهبي أو المطلق الذي يتضمن اللعبة الأساسية والتذكرة الموسمية.
 
اطلبوه مسبقاً لتتلقوا حزمة (كيسل رانر) الإضافية التي تتضمن عناصر تجميلية لـspeeder وسفينة الفضاء Trailblazer!*
 
مع مكافأة الطلب المسبق، احصلوا على حزمة (كيسل رانر) الإضافية* التي تشتمل على: 
- حزمة عناصر تجميلية لـspeeder.
- عنصر تجميلي لسفينة الفضاء Trailblazer.
 
*العرض والمحتوى والمواعيد عرضة للتغير. قد يكون المحتوى متاحاً للشراء و/أو كهدية (هدايا) بشكل منفصل وفقاً لتقدير Ubisoft فقط في أي وقت.

حول Star Wars Outlaws:
خوضوا مغامرة أول لعبة عالم مفتوح من Star Wars™ الواقعة بين أحداث The Empire Strikes Back وReturn of the Jedi. اكتشفوا كواكب مختلفة مشهورة وجديدة عبر المجرة. جازفوا بكل شيء بشخصية (كاي فيس)، محتالة ناشئة تسعى لنيل الحرية والموارد اللازمة لتبدأ حياة جديدة مع شريكها (نيكس). قاتلوا واستولوا وتفوقوا بدهاء على عصابات المجرة الإجرامية بصحبة أكثر الأشخاص المطلوبين للنظام في المجرة.

يمكن معرفة المزيد من خلال: https://starwarsoutlaws.com

عن Ubisoft:
إن Ubisoft مبتكرة عوالم، تسعى نحو إمتاع اللاعبين بتجارب أصلية ولا تُنسى. إن فرق Ubisoft العالمية تصنع وتطوّر مكتبة من الألعاب المتنوعة والثرية، وتتميز بسلاسل مثل Assassin’s Creed® وBrawlhalla® وFor Honor® وFar Cry® وTom Clancy’s Ghost Recon® وJust Dance® وRabbids® وTom Clancy’s Rainbow Six® وThe Crew® وTom Clancy’s The Division® وWatch Dogs®. عبر Ubisoft Connect، يستمتع اللاعبون بمجموعة خدمات تحسن تجارب لعبهم، اكسبوا مكافآت وتواصلوا مع أصدقائكم عبر الأجهزة المختلفة. مع خدمة اشتراك Ubisoft+، يمكنكم التوصّل إلى مكتبة ألعاب دائمة النمو تحتوي على أكثر من 100 لعبة وإضافة من Ubisoft. لعام 2021-22 المالي، حققت Ubisoft حجوزات صافية بمقدار 2.129 مليار يورو. للمزيد من التفاصيل نرجو زيارة: www.ubisoftgroup.com.

ja.title: スター・ウォーズ 無法者たち : オフィシャルストーリートレーラー
ja.description:
2024年8月30日登場。ゲーム本編とシーズンパスが含まれるゴールドエディションとアルティメットエディションは、３日間早くプレイできます。

今すぐ予約して、宇宙船「トレイルブレイザー」とスピーダーのコスメティックが含まれる「ケッセル・ランナー」ボーナスパックを受け取りましょう！*

予約特典の「ケッセル・ランナー」ボーナスパック*には以下の内容が含まれます。 
- スピーダー用のコスメティック
宇宙船「トレイルブレイザー」用のコスメティック

*オファー、内容、日程は変更される場合があります。コンテンツは、Ubisoftの独自の裁量により、いつでも個別に販売および無料配布の対象となる場合があります。

『Star Wars Outlaws™』について:
史上初オープンワールドの「スター・ウォーズ」ゲーム。時代は「スター・ウォーズ/帝国の逆襲」から「スター・ウォーズ/ジェダイの帰還」の間、本作で登場する新しい惑星やシリーズでおなじみの惑星を舞台に銀河系を探索しよう。自由と新たな人生を求める悪党「ケイ・ヴェス」となり、あらゆる冒険に挑もう。相棒の「ニックス」と一緒に戦闘や盗みの依頼を引き受け、銀河系犯罪シンジケートでうまく立ち回り、銀河系の最重要指名手配に成りあがろう。

危険を冒す覚悟さえあれば、銀河系には成りあがるチャンスが溢れている。

詳細は公式ウェブサイト: http://www.starwarsoutlaws.comをご覧ください

INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/starwarsoutlaws/
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/starwarsoutlaws
DISCORD: https://discord.gg/starwarsoutlaws

Ubisoftについて：
Ubisoftはオリジナルで思い出に残るエンターテインメント体験をプレイヤーの皆様にお届けすることを目指しています。世界中のチームが「アサシン クリード」「レインボーシックス」「ファークライ」「ジャストダンス」「ディビジョン」「ウォッチドッグス」「ザ クルー」「ラビッツ」をはじめとする多岐にわたるブランドを生み出しています。
Ubisoft Connectではゲーム体験をより豊かにし、報酬の獲得や様々なプラットフォームのフレンドとつながるサービスをお楽しみいただけます。

2022年3月決算期では売上収益21億2900万ユーロを達成しました。

snippet.title: Risk of Rain 2 - Devotion Update
snippet.description:
Wishlist Seekers of the Storm now!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2306620/Risk_of_Rain_2_Seekers_of_the_Storm/
Epic: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/risk-of-rain-2--seekers-of-the-storm

snippet.title: The 2025 Toyota 4Runner is HERE! First look
snippet.description:
The 2025 Toyota 4Runner (Pricing yet to be announced) is all-new and is now on Toyota’s newest global truck platform. It comes standard with a 2.4L turbo 4-cylinder engine making 278 horsepower and 317 lb-ft of torque, but the i-FORCE MAX option adds a hybrid powertrain which is good for 326 horsepower and a strong 465 lb-ft of torque. Thomas and James are excited to have a first look inside and out of the new Toyota 4Runner, and see what the new generation has to offer. We hope you enjoy the episode. SUBSCRIBE!

snippet.title: WARRIORS at LAKERS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | April 9, 2024
snippet.description:
Never miss a moment with the latest news, trending stories and highlights to bring you closer to your favorite players and teams.
Download now: https://link.nba.com/NBAYouTube

The Golden State Warriors defeated the Los Angeles Lakers 134-120. Klay Thompson recorded 27 points, 5 3PM, and 3 assists for the Warriors, with Stephen Curry adding 23 points (6-6 3PM), 8 assists, and 7 rebounds in the victory. LeBron James tallied 33 points, 11 assists, and 7 rebounds for the Lakers. The Warriors improve to 44-35, while the Lakers fall to 45-35.

With their performance tonight (26-41 - 63.4%), the Warriors become the first team in NBA history to make 25+ 3PT FGs AND shoot 60% or better on 3PT attempts.
Previously, the highest mark for a team was 59.5% (25-42) from the Memphis Grizzlies on 3/24/2023

snippet.title: The Beach Boys | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for an endless summer of fun, fun, fun with “The Beach Boys,” the all-new documentary streaming exclusively on Disney+ beginning May 24, 2024. And be sure to check out the trailer and key art out today and share them with your readers!   
 
“The Beach Boys” is a celebration of the legendary band that revolutionized pop music, and the iconic, harmonious sound they created that personified the California dream, captivating fans for generations and generations to come. The documentary traces the band from humble family beginnings and features never-before-seen footage and all-new interviews with The Beach Boys’ Brian Wilson, Mike Love, Al Jardine, David Marks, Bruce Johnston, plus other luminaries in the music business, including Lindsey Buckingham, Janelle Monáe, Ryan Tedder, and Don Was. Viewers will also hear from the group’s Carl and Dennis Wilson in their own words, plus view a new interview with Blondie Chaplin and hear audio from Ricky Fataar. A Kennedy/Marshall and White Horse Pictures Production, “The Beach Boys” is directed by Frank Marshall and Thom Zimny and written by Mark Monroe. The film is produced by Frank Marshall, Irving Azoff, Nicholas Ferrall, Jeanne Elfant Festa, Aly Parker, with Nigel Sinclair, Mark Monroe, Tony Rosenthal, Cassidy Hartmann, Glen Zipper, Thom Zimny, Beth Collins, Jimmy Edwards, Susan Genco, Marc Cimino, Jody Gerson, Bruce Resnikoff, and Ben J. Murphy serving as executive producers.

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/WaltDisneyStudios
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/disneystudios/
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@disneystudios
X: https://twitter.com/disneystudios

snippet.title: 2024 Honorary Starters at the Masters
snippet.description:
Watch the Honorary Starters, a tradition dating to 1963. #themasters 

---

Since 1934, the Masters Tournament has been home to some of golf’s greatest moments. Amidst blooming azaleas, towering pines and flowering dogwoods, the first full week of April ushers in a stage unique to golf and to sport. Over four days and 72 holes, the smallest field in major championship golf competes for a chance to capture the Green Jacket and a place in Masters history.

---

snippet.title: Pushpa 2 The Rule Teaser | Allu Arjun | Sukumar | Rashmika Mandanna | Fahadh Faasil | DSP
snippet.description:
Pushpa 2 The Rule Teaser on Mythri Movie Makers. 

Pushpa 2 - The Rule - Written and Directed by Sukumar. Produced by Naveen Yerneni and Y. Ravi Shankar of Mythri Movie Makers in association with Sukumar Writings,  the film stars Allu Arjun, Fahadh Faasil, Rashmika Mandanna, Dhanunjay, Rao Ramesh, Sunil, Anasuya Bharadwaj & Ajay Ghosh. The film's music is composed by Devi Sri Prasad.

Wishing our Pushpa Raj aka Icon stAAr Allu Arjun a very Happy Birthday 🥳 #HappyBirthdayAlluArjun

snippet.title: UConn vs. Purdue - 2024 men's National Championship extended highlights
snippet.description:
UConn capped off one of the most dominant NCAA tournament runs of all time, defeating Purdue 75-60 to claim it's sixth national championship in program history. The Huskies became the first program to repeat as national champions since Florida in 2006-07. Watch the extended highlights from the 2024 National Championship here.

Watch highlights, game recaps and much more from the NCAA Division I men’s and women’s basketball tournaments on the official NCAA March Madness YouTube channel. Subscribe now to be updated on the latest videos: https://www.youtube.com/marchmadness

snippet.title: FLY ME TO THE MOON - Official Trailer (HD)
snippet.description:
The whole world will be watching. #FlyMeToTheMoon starring Scarlett Johansson and Channing Tatum – coming exclusively to movie theaters this July.

Visit Our Website:
http://flymetothemoon.movie/

Follow Us on Social:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/FlyMeMovie
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/flymetothemoon/ 
X: https://twitter.com/FlyMeMovie 
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@flymetothemoon 

Starring Scarlett Johansson and Channing Tatum, FLY ME TO THE MOON is a sharp, stylish comedy-drama set against the high-stakes backdrop of NASA’s historic Apollo 11 moon landing. Brought in to fix NASA’s public image, sparks fly in all directions as marketing maven Kelly Jones (Johansson) wreaks havoc on launch director Cole Davis’s (Tatum) already difficult task. When the White House deems the mission too important to fail, Jones is directed to stage a fake moon landing as back-up and the countdown truly begins…

Directed by:     
Greg Berlanti

Screenplay by:     
Rose Gilroy

Based upon the story by:    
Bill Kirstein & Keenan Flynn

Produced by:      
Scarlett Johansson
Jonathan Lia
Keenan Flynn
Sarah Schechter

Executive Producer:
Robert J. Dohrmann

Cast:       
Scarlett Johansson 
Channing Tatum
Nick Dillenburg 
Anna Garcia
Jim Rash
Noah Robbins
Colin Woodell
Christian Zuber 
Donald Elise Watkins
with Ray Romano
and Woody Harrelson

snippet.title: Epic Gender Reveal Surprise for our Twins! (Shocked)
snippet.description:
GENDER REVEAL TWINS STYLE....This is our 3rd gender reveal party, and we wanted to make it extra special considering there is an extra baby inside. The test that we took sent back the results super fast, which we had mailed to our amazing friends Ruth and Scott. We wanted to include both our kids in the reveal, and found the cutest way to have them reveal the gender of their future siblings. The results were NOT what we expected!!!

#genderreveal  #pregnancyannouncement  #twins  #momlife  #baby  #firsttrimester  #genderrevealparty #parenting #surprise

👋 Hello everyone and welcome to Hanging with the Hehners!

I'm Jamie Otis Hehner and me and my hubby of 10 years, Doug Hehner met & married on the same day as strangers on season 1 of Lifetime TV's Married At First Sight.

We lost our first baby, Johnathan.👼🏼 While trying to grow our family, we lost a couple more babies. ➡️ Sooo, we feel exceptionally thankful for our two beautiful rainbow babies: Henley & Hendrix.

Now we are embarking on a fun new adventure that hopefully helps us grow stronger as husband & wife, but also closer to our kiddos.
We are SO EXCITED for this wild, new experience & we can't wait to take YOU along the ride! 
➡️  So, on this channel, we share content on love, family, marriage, and lifestyle. We love to keep it real and fun (our subscribers can attest to this). We share our wins, losses, rock bottoms, and milestones with the aim of spreading love and positivity.👪✨

We're taking a risky step into the unknown, and we'd like to invite you to join us! ❤️
So, hit that “Subscribe” button and “ring” the bell to never miss a video.
